{
  "name": "RPlog_Lover_s_Quarrel_in_the_Dome",
  "title": "Lover's Quarrel in the Dome",
  "summary": "At the famous Free-Flight Dance Dome on Etti IV, the watchful Simone Drake settles in at the bar just as a furious Sean Dillon storms in, scattering patrons and drinking heavily to drown his temper. The bouncer Landis tenses, recognizing the Direx Board man and unsure whether to intervene as a curious crowd gathers around Dillon's outburst. The poised Lady Alora arrives and confronts Dillon, coolly ordering the club's hired muscle to leave and demonstrating a chilling, unseen power that drops one man choking to the floor. Dillon glowers but reacts with eerie indifference as Alora dismisses his threats and departs without a backward glance. Simone watches the whole confrontation with amused detachment from the far end of the bar before Dillon finally drains his drink and stalks out into the Port District.",
